size.description: Changes the size to small or large.
size.name: size

color.description:
Determines the color of the icon. Some icons have a default system colour
like quotes, jobs, and invoices. Others that doesn't have a system colour
falls back to greyBlueDark.
color.name: color

customColor.description: Sets a custom color for the icon. Can be a rgb() or hex value.
customColor.name: customColor

testID.description: Used to locate this view in end-to-end tests
